metadata.name: ChillTuna #1
metadata.description:
Among the weird-looking devices in the underwater lab, these bottles specially designed by Conner have been found – pay attention to the ones made of precious materials - Nun. Elixir collecting skill is ACTIVATED now. Come with me to Tunarcadia to collect Elixir! 

Oh! You might wanna collect as much as possible because rumor has it that Elixir is the key token in the great Chill Tuna ecosystem – related to SLG and utility upgrades and more!
